             was indicted for <rs id="t18040516-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040516-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18040516-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the 9th of May, six silver spoons, value 6 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18040516-1-victim50" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Incledon
                  <interp inst="t18040516-1-victim50" type="surname" value="Incledon"></interp>
